<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>DejaGnu</application></title>

<para>Install <application>DejaGnu</application> by running the following 
commands:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install &amp;&amp;
make install-doc</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

<sect2>
<title>Contents</title>

<para>The <application>DejaGnu</application> package contains 
<command>runtest</command>.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2><title>Description</title>

<sect3><title>runtest</title>
<para><command>runtest</command> is the <application>DejaGnu</application> 
test driver program; use it to  control what tests to run, and variations on 
how to run them.</para></sect3>

